<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For My Shasha ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
}

body{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9ecf,#ffd6e8);
overflow:hidden;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:40px;
border-radius:25px;
text-align:center;
width:90%;
max-width:450px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
animation:fade 2s;
}

h1{
color:#ff4081;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

button{
padding:15px 35px;
font-size:20px;
border:none;
border-radius:50px;
background:#ff4081;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
transform:scale(1.1);
}

#answer{
display:none;
margin-top:20px;
font-size:28px;
color:#e91e63;
font-weight:bold;
}

@keyframes fade{
from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);}
to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
color:#ff4d88;
font-size:24px;
animation:float 8s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(100vh);
opacity:0;
}
20%{opacity:1;}
100%{
transform:translateY(-120vh);
opacity:0;
}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<h1>💖 To My Shasha My Janam ❣️ Queen 👸</h1>

<p>
Every heartbeat reminds me of you.<br><br>

Your smile is my favorite place.<br>

Your happiness means everything to me.<br><br>

I never want to imagine a future without you.
</p>

<h2>Will You Be My Girlfriend? ❤️</h2>

<br>

<button onclick="yes()">YES 💍</button>

<div id="answer">
🥹❤️ You just made me the happiest person alive! ❤️🥹
</div>

</div>

<script>

function yes(){
document.getElementById("answer").style.display="block";
}

function hearts(){

let h=document.createElement("div");

h.className="heart";

h.innerHTML="❤️";

h.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";

h.style.fontSize=(20+Math.random()*30)+"px";

h.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*5)+"s";

document.body.appendChild(h);

setTimeout(()=>h.remove(),9000);

}

setInterval(hearts,300);

</script>

</body>
</html>
